_sText: Aim_ag_radical2 ----------- 12 players or less (preferred) Description: A simple skill map set within a medium outdoor arena with objects placed tactically forcing you to use skill to eliminate your enemies. This is a texture map. Use the height and cover to your advantage. I made this map to a design from a friend (radical). This is his second design and was really fun to play. Objective: Use the objects and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve.
